She took a break from her hermit status and hopped on a private jet to show her mother some love.

Swift kept things casual in lose-fitted clothing, and at one point she was spotted in shorts so tiny they looked like underwear.

Peek-a-boo Tay's booty!

The pop artist is also rumored to be "secretly dating" Brit actor Joe Alwyn. Perhaps that's why she's been so undercover.
